74294a9df","tid":20752,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好玩，一日玩唔晒<br />\n第一次去果時覺得好似入左kingdom heart世界"},{"pid":"1f0286e29847ee554f5fada8bf63e2a7e5e90969","tid":20752,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T20:00:56.000Z","msg":"同香港比 當然值，俍疇都唔同D."},{"pid":"608e599ae0c833f3910e561cc49e184ef19aca29","tid":20752,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T20:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同香港比 當然值，俍疇都唔同D.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食野都唔同D. 餐廳靚好多。"},{"pid":"e7b3ad299c852c16a5f6c8a5e7351b457abc46c6","tid":20752,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:47:48.000Z","msg":"日本自理，不受迪士尼控制<br />\n<br />\n去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f08a4d3b906d02c96360e7c0fbc31466580245","tid":20752,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"去，氣氛超正<br />\n<br />\n記得狗衝拎胡迪fp 先"},{"pid":"6abe162527b43e0a015fd8f02170d9580aee4c2b","tid":20752,"uid":10007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:59:52.000Z","msg":"Disneyland sea好好玩 好有新鮮感<br />\n但disneyland non-sea 同香港一樣咁"},{"pid":"1c51479a8371e392466715e10bb696cd362df7e4","tid":20752,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:00:43.000Z","msg":"未去過值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931fd0ed87f262d55b6c5d3a6dea05c6c2da4e5c","tid":20752,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"Sea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c5d35d2bcbc0efb827e55f3f295ecd8452d0c3","tid":20752,"uid":40310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"淨係 sea 都一日玩唔晒，因為樣樣野都要勁排隊，可能因為我去嗰日係星期日，又遲出發，去到已經接近11點。我記得連啲fastpass都俾人攞晒"},{"pid":"300373d153a3e63e456773e662c184df21cb56b8","tid":20752,"uid":37595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"本身唔太好迪士尼野，但日本真心好氣氛，好值得去"},{"pid":"91ec59388fbf2c1fe4f82a5666d565e5be2b3df2","tid":20752,"uid":50025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"決定去DisneySea，thank you all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9ea5088362b305a12e4f73f069f87336ed08b9","tid":20752,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"香港迪士尼好悶"},{"pid":"12ea8a5c316098d3d21e67d760247b65766413a1","tid":20752,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7e8SuNq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7e8SuNq.jpg&h=db503b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後便座野必玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個當年去果時冇做攻課，唔知乜黎，見到唔駛排隊咪去玩囉。<br />\n入到去坐低，以為係玩體感過山車，搖黎搖去果類。<br />\n一直睇片見到故事入邊架會跌落去就心知不妙，突然開前邊窗，見到街外，我就知今次仆街了。<br />\n<br />\n結果今次跳樓機玩得好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0e2319226582c99fe7d1c6a3da3cd56fb24b08","tid":20752,"uid":22676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7e8SuNq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7e8SuNq.jpg&h=db503b8b&s={SIZE}\" />後便座野必玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係！真係好好玩<br />\n我排左1個鐘"},{"pid":"3ba8ec1fe88a0ac665a3349b0f716c5826fef5ac","tid":20752,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:38:34.000Z","msg":"仆街一開園狗衝拎胡迪fp,淨係拎fp 都排半粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後由上面失落三角洲玩番落黎<br />\n<br />\n最可惜係未到中午，跳樓機fp 已經派晒，直到收園，排隊時間維持係120分鐘，即係唔駛玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c93f7e4567f75f6736fa6d324098dc079fd2c0","tid":20752,"uid":50025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆街一開園狗衝拎胡迪fp,淨係拎fp 都排半粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後由上面失落三角洲玩番落黎<br />\n<br />\n最可惜係未到中午，跳樓機fp 已經派晒，直到收園，排隊時間維持係120分鐘，即係唔駛玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n星期幾去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771ab77cbcae60324598b37ddfae9ac008a1163a","tid":20752,"uid":47383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:11:59.000Z","msg":"唔值得去 排隊都排撚死你 就算攞完fast pass都要等幾個鐘後先有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次同男朋友玩左2個機動遊戲就已經無左成日"},{"pid":"7e3c6b21e7aa60f63b9e5c51fd01caa5b02beb95","tid":20752,"uid":1485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T21:19:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7e8SuNq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7e8SuNq.jpg&h=db503b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後便座野必玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個當年去果時冇做攻課，唔知乜黎，見到唔駛排隊咪去玩囉。<br />\n入到去坐低，以為係玩體感過山車，搖黎搖去果類。<br />\n一直睇片見到故事入邊架會跌落去就心知不妙，突然開前邊窗，見到街外，我就知今次仆街了。<br />\n<br />\n結果今次跳樓機玩得好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都同你一樣，以為係排鬼屋，<br />\n你又點會估得到玩跳樓機會用一條好似私家車嘅安全帶就算，仲要叫你就咁放個袋係地下，陰到我應一應，應該成車都係日本人，得我哋兩個乜Q都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一打開窗果下，就知今次仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}